*******************************************************************************
       Name: Condemn
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 15
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: The weight of condemnation lifts from you.
Acquisition:
   - Sentinel: level 45
Description:
   Condemn is the Sentinel's highest judgment technique. The warrior formally
   condemns the target, invoking the Pale Ledger's authority to mark them as
   a declared enemy. The condemned target suffers a persistent debuff that
   reduces all their combat stats, representing the psychological and
   metaphysical weight of being formally condemned.

   While Condemned, the target takes increased damage from Sentinel attacks
   and has reduced effectiveness in all combat actions. The effect of Condemn
   is difficult to remove, as it represents a formal ruling rather than a
   temporary magical effect. Condemn is most powerful as a sustained pressure
   tool in lengthy battles where the cumulative debuff significantly shifts
   the balance of combat.
*******************************************************************************
